attributes.description: This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of threat intelligence events detected in the user's environment using Google Threat Intelligence IOC stream data.

params.markdown:
[Threat Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-9e8de699-a623-4a1b-9f63-7d641116f531) | [Adversary Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-0b0fb6b4-d250-4e31-a56a-bb872e4c7c4a) | [Threat Feed Overview](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-95187e5c-b4a2-45ad-b6a4-d6ce68e1f43e) |**IOC Stream Threat Intelligence** | [IOC Stream Overview](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-fb3daf8e-b45b-4fd9-bf94-dbaf96fcfb67)

This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of threat intelligence events detected using Google Threat Intelligence IOC Stream data. It delivers insights into event distribution, threat analysis, and categorized breakdowns by threat indicator type, severity, and verdict, including detected events over time.

Key metrics include total detected events and unique files, URLs, domains, and IPs. Advanced filtering allows refinement by indicator type, threat score, verdict, and severity. Events are further analyzed by file types, countries, and tags to identify patterns.

Network and organizational insights highlight the top 10 autonomous system owners, and IPv4 network ranges. Additionally, it identifies the top 10 source event datasets and modules. Saved searches streamline investigations by summarizing detected file, IP, URL, and domain events.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/ti_google_threat_intelligence/overview)
